  "title": "Hair Therapist | Islandwide | Gross up to $4,500 + Benefits",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Duties and Responsibilities</strong>:</h3><p>As a Hair Therapist, you will:</p><ul><li>Deliver scalp treatments, shampooing, and blow-dry styling for customers.</li><li>Ensure cleanliness and adherence to workplace safety standards.</li><li>Collaborate with consultants to monitor customer treatment progress and build strong customer relationships.</li><li>Assist customers in selecting suitable retail products or services tailored to their hair care needs.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul><h3><strong>Qualifications and Attributes</strong>:</h3><p>We are looking for individuals who:</p><ul><li>Are bilingual in <strong>Chinese</strong> and <strong>English</strong> for effective communication with diverse customers.</li><li>Possess <strong>excellent communication skills</strong>.</li><li>Are <strong>team players</strong> with a positive attitude.</li><li>No prior experience is required—<strong>training will be provided</strong>!</li></ul><h3><strong>Working Hours & Pattern:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Weekdays:</strong> 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM or 12:00 PM – 9:00 PM</li><li><strong>Weekends and Public Holidays:</strong> 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM</li><li><strong>Work Week Pattern:</strong> 6/5/6/5, totaling <strong>44 working hours per week</strong></li></ul><h3><strong>Annual Leave and Benefits:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Annual Leave:</strong> 10 days</li><li>Comprehensive <strong>medical and dental benefits</strong></li><li>Clear <strong>career progression opportunities</strong></li></ul><p>EA Personnel Name: Nicholas Wong</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23113643</p><p>EA License No: 23C1703</p>",
